oai_dc:dc.dc:title: REEF RUNWAY WAVE PROTECTIVE STRUCTURE, HONOLULU INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT, OAHU, HAWAII, STABILITY PERFORMANCE EVALUATION
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Chun, Robert S.
Noda, Edward K.
Tamaye, Elaine E.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: protective structure
Honolulu International Airport
structure stability
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An inspection survey of the Reef Runway Wave Protective Structure at the Honolulu International Airport was accomplished in 1982 to access the performance of the dolos and rock armored structure to date. The inspection showed the structure to be performing adequately considering that the design wave conditions were experienced.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Coastal Engineering Proceedings; No. 19 (1984): Proceedings of 19th Conference on Coastal Engineering, Houston, Texas, 1984.; 181
